    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i know, i know. people always say that. but it doesn't feel like a \"crisis\" or anything... it just feels like a fact. like, if you take away everything that made me *me*, what's actually left? there's just this empty space where a person used to be. it's hard to even see a point in trying to rebuild when the foundation is completely destroyed.",
