      "content": "it's just so exhausting to keep pretending. everyone looks at me and sees this success, this perfect version, and they have no idea none of that actually exists anymore. it feels like i'm just a ghost haunting my own life. how can i stay here when the person who was supposed to live this life is already gone?",
